1
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:42,000
Ge Zhendong sent me here.

2
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:42,880
The evidence.

3
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,439
It's by the bed at the guesthouse.

4
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:47,439
Where's Dali?

5
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,679
He's preparing a surprise for you.

6
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:50,679
Where are we going?

7
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,280
Jing'an Guesthouse.

8
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,320
Got it.

9
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,399
Hai, Weiwei!

10
00:01:00,399 --> 00:01:01,479
I'm back.

11
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:06,719
Weiwei?

12
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:08,760
Hai?

13
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,159
Where is everyone?

14
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:21,640
You're not dressed warm enough.

15
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,319
Such a thoughtful kid.

16
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:28,519
Why isn't the bus here yet?

17
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:29,920
What's the rush?

18
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,879
He's a grown man, no one's gonna kidnap him.

19
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:34,920
Can't you say something nice?

20
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,959
But why does my right eye keep twitching?

21
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:45,719
Nothing bad's gonna happen, right?

22
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:52,200
What's going on?

23
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,079
We're screwed.

24
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,400
Dali was here.

25
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:54,799
Let's go!

26
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:55,120
Move!

27
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,239
Where's the money?

28
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,760
That was the money for the orders!

29
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:04,920
Director Ge.

30
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,120
Are you okay?

31
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,519
Why wouldn't I be?

32
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,159
It's gone.

33
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,120
It's all gone.

34
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,280
I just got an anonymous tip.

35
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:13,840
Saying that Zhu Yihai

36
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,919
stole money from the factory.

37
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,879
How could it be him?

38
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,120
Why would he steal the factory's money?

39
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,039
Section Chief Dao.

40
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,680
You need to go find him right now.

41
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,719
Those are public funds.

42
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:22,919
I can't cover this up!

43
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:23,800
On it.

44
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,560
Hurry up!

45
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,360
Wait

46
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:40,240
What's this?

47
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,199
Zhu Yihai

48
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,080
Someone reported

49
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,360
that Zhu Yihai stole money from our factory

50
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,120
Where is he?

51
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,240
Oh, damn it

52
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,719
Qiangzi

53
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,439
After him!

54
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,439
Don't let that punk get away

55
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:58,639
Go!

56
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:03,960
Xiong Dali

57
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,719
Slow down

58
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,120
Xiong Dali

59
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,439
Slow down

60
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:18,840
Stop!

61
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,680
Slow down a bit

62
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,080
Stop right there

63
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:26,719
Stop!

64
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,680
Stop right now!

65
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,400
Xiong Dali

66
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:36,960
Xiong Dali

67
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:38,680
Little brat

68
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:39,879
Stop running

69
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,800
Stop chasing me!

70
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,159
I'm done chasing

71
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,400
Stop chasing

72
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,319
You stop running too

73
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,439
Alright

74
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:48,520
Buddy

75
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,479
Look at you, barely wearing anything

76
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:51,919
You must be exhausted

77
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,039
What are you looking at?

78
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,319
After him!

79
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,680
Slow down, slow down, Dali

80
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,560
Xie Fan

81
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:25,000
Can't you knock?

82
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,680
Someone sent me to find you

83
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,560
Who?

84
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,560
Secretary Yu

85
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:51,240
So you're here to threaten me?

86
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,160
Threaten?

87
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,000
Brother

88
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,480
If you had just given me

89
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,600
Aimin Street, which belongs to me,

90
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,439
there wouldn't be all this trouble

91
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,759
Am I right?

92
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,560
Brother Xie Fan,

93
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:08,959
My fault

94
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:09,959
Of course

95
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:10,639
Don't get mad

96
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:11,759
Come, sit down

97
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:12,920
Come on, come on

98
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,800
Sit, trust me

99
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,759
I was wondering what the big deal was

100
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,439
Making such a fuss

101
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:18,920
Come

102
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:19,839
Come sit

103
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:23,360
I know

104
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,839
you're upset

105
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:27,120
I know I wronged you recently

106
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,519
But think about it

107
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,279
If I hadn't done that

108
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,920
Zhu Yihai

109
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,079
why would he help me deal with Ge Zhendong?

110
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,800
Brother Xie Fan,

111
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,160
How many years have we known each other?

112
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,680
How could I ever sacrifice you?

113
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,560
Besides

114
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,560
the contract for Aimin Street

115
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,800
I already have it in my hands

116
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,360
Zhu Yihai

117
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,600
He's of no use anymore

118
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,120
Once I get rid of him

119
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,439
I'll let you

120
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,759
take back everything that was yours

121
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,040
Dali, stop blocking the door

122
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:07,000
Open the door

123
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,199
Dali

124
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,680
Section Chief Dao

125
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,040
He locked the door

126
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,319
You guys up there

127
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,879
Pry this door open!

128
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,160
Put some muscle into it!

129
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,959
Get this door open!

130
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,279
Dali

131
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:30,800
Damn it

132
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,680
Why are they still on my tail?

133
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,959
I fell right into that woman's trap

134
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:38,439
Zhu Yihai, Zhu Yihai

135
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,240
Please don't let it be you

136
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,199
Those are public funds

137
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:42,879
Stealing public funds

138
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:44,079
That'll get you locked up

139
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:48,759
Dali, don't do anything stupid

140
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:53,879
I'm freezing to death

141
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,079
I-I-I'm not waiting for you

142
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:55,920
Hey, sir

143
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,639
Give me a ride

144
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,319
What am I supposed to do if you leave?

145
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,519
I'm leaving, I'm freezing!

146
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:01,000
What about me?

147
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,560
Can I just sit on the crossbar then?

148
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,879
Running keeps you warm

149
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,279
My gloves

150
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,519
Little brat

151
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,720
Let's see where you can run now

152
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:18,519
Stay back

153
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,639
Don't come any closer!

154
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,759
Dali

155
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,680
Don't you move

156
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,319
I'm not moving

157
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,759
I'm not moving

158
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,160
Mom

159
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,639
I've let you down, Mom

160
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,120
Dali

161
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,000
Dali

162
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:37,959
Dali

163
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:39,680
Throw that bag down to me

164
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:41,639
Dali

165
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:42,879
Here

166
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,600
Huilian

167
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,360
Hurry, go after him!

168
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,079
Get back here

169
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,240
Chase him? Are you crazy?

170
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,600
If anyone sees this

171
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,079
we'll be accomplices

172
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,439
You think I don't know?

173
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,759
Over there

174
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,279
Half an hour and still no sign of him

175
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,519
Don't worry, we'll find him

176
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,959
Zhu Yihai, oh Zhu Yihai

177
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,959
You really are a handful

178
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,399
Director Ge

179
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,160
Dahai

180
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,279
Missed me, didn't you?

181
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,199
What's this?

182
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,279
I just found it

183
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,160
You found it?

184
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,799
What is this?

185
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,480
Money

186
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,039
Is this my money?

187
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,480
Keep better track of your stuff next time

188
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,039
It really is my money

189
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,600
Thanks, man.

190
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,840
We're buddies.

191
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,399
Take it.

192
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,159
So you're Zhu Yihai.

193
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:28,960
Who are you?

194
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:32,039
You've pulled plenty of stunts while I was away.

195
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,200
No.

196
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,480
It's all a misunderstanding.

197
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,240
You believe everything they say?

198
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,159
Listen to me on this.

199
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,840
What do you mean?

200
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,120
Director Ge.

201
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,639
I'd call this returning what's found.

202
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:42,120
Right.

203
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,519
Shouldn't you give me a commendation banner?

204
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,120
I will.

205
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:44,799
Absolutely.

206
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,799
Scoundrel.

207
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,600
Little girl, you keep calling me

208
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,919
a scoundrel. What do you mean?

209
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,399
You listen to me.

210
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:57,039
I'm not going to put up with your nonsense.

211
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,639
Your good days

212
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,360
are over today.

213
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,840
Don't think signing the Transfer Agreement

214
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,879
lets you do whatever you want.

215
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,720
I'm officially notifying you now.

216
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,600
If your demolition compensation

217
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,600
doesn't arrive within a week,

218
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,440
the Transfer Agreement

219
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,159
will be immediately void.

220
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,440
Who the hell are you?

221
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:27,639
Your nemesis.

